  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Jamuy Dios kay sonqosniykuman./
 /Kallpata qoway, munakuytapis;
 Qhatisqaykitaj, tukuy sonqowan./
 
[V2]
 /Oh Diosniy, Qan Yanapariway./
 /Jucha saqeyta ni atiymanchu;
 Atiykiykiwan Qan yanapariway./
 
</lyrics></song>